Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.71,0:00:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新機動戰記-鋼彈W]\NJust Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.31,0:00:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.78,0:00:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.32,0:00:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.43,0:00:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱著你被淋濕的肩膀 想溫暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.64,0:00:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,顫抖的指尖 徬徨地在找甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.44,0:00:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留住你的視線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.72,0:01:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信把悲傷變為力量的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.16,0:01:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.83,0:01:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.47,0:01:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.17,0:01:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.67,0:01:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,離開地球的人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.77,0:01:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在宇宙殖民衛星的生活裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.17,0:01:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尋找新的希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.51,0:01:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，地球圈統一聯合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.34,0:01:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,藉正義及和平為名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.38,0:01:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以壓倒性的軍事力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.58,0:01:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,壓制著各個殖民衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.02,0:01:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ac195年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.66,0:01:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作戰名稱[流星作戰]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.19,0:01:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和聯合反目的部份衛星居民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.83,0:01:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決定把偽裝為流星的新武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.73,0:01:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,送落地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.67,0:01:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，這次作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.84,0:01:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早已被聯合總部發覺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.01,0:02:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太…太過份…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.01,0:02:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會殺死你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.02,0:02:18.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二話\N[人稱死神的鋼彈]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.80,0:02:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我聽到了，希洛同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.00,0:02:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你昨日撕爛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.24,0:02:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜小姐的邀請卡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.74,0:02:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你為何要做那種事呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.84,0:02:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我身為同學也覺得憤怒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.88,0:02:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你身為男子漢\N不覺得羞恥的嗎!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.26,0:02:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次起長話短說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.30,0:03:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趁你還有命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.27,0:03:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才的是希洛同學!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.34,0:03:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的確是他啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.84,0:03:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他好利害，雖然外表不像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.42,0:03:19.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慢吞吞在做甚麼!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.32,0:03:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為不是機動戰士專用艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.99,0:03:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以須要時間部署
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.79,0:03:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之把所有水中機動戰士放落海中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.63,0:03:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長，SMS的傑克斯特尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.06,0:03:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有通訊來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.70,0:03:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯的寵兒有甚麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.57,0:03:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來很棘手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.53,0:03:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和你無關!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.30,0:03:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的說話...我明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.27,0:03:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，如果工程沒大進展
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.11,0:03:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我恐怕那會影響聯合總部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.01,0:03:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對艦長你的能力評價
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.45,0:03:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亂講!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.98,0:03:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.32,0:03:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們正在用新型潛水母艦航行中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.72,0:03:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但引擎有問題正頭痛著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.92,0:03:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別想要軍隊浪費無謂的錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.02,0:04:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.36,0:04:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想你替我們的潛水母艦修理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.76,0:04:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我的空母嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.43,0:04:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.90,0:04:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當作報答你，我會借給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.60,0:04:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的最新水中機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.30,0:04:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[派西斯]和[坎沙]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.64,0:04:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此，你讓我領功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.08,0:04:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要我對故障一事守口如瓶吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.74,0:04:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你意下如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.21,0:04:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧，你快點上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.21,0:04:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.62,0:04:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯特尉，這艘艦完全正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.69,0:04:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不那樣說他不會同意我們協助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.26,0:04:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們重視實績多過名聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.34,0:04:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家，人到齊了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.04,0:04:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，開始上馬術課
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.88,0:04:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今日，我們直接實習\N來談談如何讓馬原地打轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.28,0:04:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛同學呢?他不在?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.32,0:05:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他老是神出鬼沒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.26,0:05:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為他馬術好...根本不需要上馬術課
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.78,0:05:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用這個就能毀滅它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.68,0:05:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,深海用魚雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.25,0:05:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能夠誘導追蹤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.39,0:05:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,海軍的武器庫嗎?距離不遠...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.46,0:05:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟著是細部調整
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.96,0:05:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛的入學費未繳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.80,0:05:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,取消
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.60,0:05:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住宿費未繳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.10,0:05:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,取消
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.23,0:05:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,學校援助金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.94,0:05:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,修改
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.87,0:05:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搜查希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.04,0:05:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.01,0:05:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見，莉莉娜小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.64,0:06:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們明天打擾妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.01,0:06:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.88,0:06:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜小姐，有甚麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.49,0:06:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那種無精打采的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.25,0:06:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是難得的生日嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.36,0:06:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請笑一下，莉莉娜小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.99,0:06:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多謝大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.27,0:06:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有秘密的男孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.71,0:06:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很多秘密，所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.18,0:06:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,秘密被知道，所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.08,0:06:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.32,0:06:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要死!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.49,0:06:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳在看可怕的\N懸疑小說嗎，小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.26,0:06:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.06,0:06:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果三枚這種魚雷直接擊中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.23,0:06:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就能誘導自爆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.23,0:06:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在它被OZ奪去前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.23,0:06:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要毀滅它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.07,0:06:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要了結一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.67,0:07:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯特尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.71,0:07:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,深海5500的位置有金屬反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.44,0:07:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，出動坎沙和派西斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.91,0:07:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特尉，請讓我出擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.65,0:07:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.08,0:07:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙和深海的情況不同啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.35,0:07:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道，請你交給我去辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.02,0:07:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，拜託你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.00,0:07:25.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,派西斯出動後，坎沙跟著出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.76,0:07:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來指揮   知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.01,0:07:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯特尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.21,0:07:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發現海軍機動戰士的反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.91,0:07:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個艦長發覺了\N我們的行動嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.08,0:07:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爆炸?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.22,0:07:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在和我們相同的深度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.62,0:07:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,機動戰士相繼被擊毀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.82,0:07:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停航，查清楚情況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.49,0:07:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,派西斯和坎沙怎樣!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.22,0:07:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊，叫他們先行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.56,0:07:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,究竟發生甚麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.34,0:08:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵襲!但不能確認敵人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.98,0:08:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有機動戰士沒有回音!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.92,0:08:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向這地點投擲爆雷!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.19,0:08:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯特尉的\N潛水母艦在那深度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.19,0:08:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別管!敵人可能就是那小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.03,0:08:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發射!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.75,0:08:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦隊開始了爆雷攻擊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.22,0:08:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無能的男人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.89,0:08:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常嘈吵，發生甚麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.79,0:08:59.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心，敵人看來在附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.83,0:09:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那部鋼彈不會還能動吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.36,0:09:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會，但別大意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.97,0:09:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣，被這麼多爆雷擊中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.70,0:09:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人一定支持不住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.37,0:09:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼事!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.21,0:09:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死吧，看見我的人全部都要死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.73,0:10:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.03,0:10:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今日難得大家為了我齊聚一堂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.27,0:10:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜真是不勝感激
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.10,0:10:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜小姐，生日快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.34,0:10:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,生日快樂!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.48,0:10:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多謝大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.18,0:10:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸，你真的要出去嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.78,0:10:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不能為了\N莉莉娜留多一會嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.35,0:10:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.89,0:10:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.29,0:10:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起，莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.06,0:10:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別介意，爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.96,0:10:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白你的苦衷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.19,0:10:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.63,0:10:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.41,0:10:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些相片…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.08,0:10:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新聞時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.41,0:11:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根據軍隊的公佈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.21,0:11:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,墜落在世界五處地方的隕石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.25,0:11:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大部份已經被燒毀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.92,0:11:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且，它們不是傳聞中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.79,0:11:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殖民衛星的人造物體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.70,0:11:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,騙人的，希洛一定在那裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.93,0:11:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，那麼希洛是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.14,0:11:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,星星王子?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.84,0:11:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.91,0:11:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要遲到莉莉娜小姐的派對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.19,0:11:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才的是希洛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.89,0:11:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.06,0:11:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ已經開始行動，趕得及嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.84,0:12:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼!?你想加入我們?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.18,0:12:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有經驗嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.22,0:12:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種東西，甚麼也不知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.73,0:12:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.23,0:12:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼回事!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.50,0:12:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,牠不會攻擊不是敵人的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.97,0:12:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,野獸很單純的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.85,0:12:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這男孩真古怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.47,0:13:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特爾少爺，飲品我拿來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.48,0:13:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麻煩你，請放在那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.45,0:13:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你覺得地球怎樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.28,0:13:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好美麗，非常，非常美麗呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.33,0:13:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然…地球這麼美麗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.24,0:13:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.44,0:13:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,物資搬去哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.91,0:13:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放在這裡就行   這種地方!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.31,0:13:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這種地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.28,0:13:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把大量物資\N交給一個小孩做甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.82,0:13:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要問，我已收了貨車的費用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.25,0:13:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.99,0:13:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麻煩你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.67,0:14:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜小姐，來，吹熄它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.10,0:14:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來，莉莉娜小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.07,0:14:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吹熄蠟燭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.57,0:14:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.28,0:14:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好像趕得及主要的項目呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.85,0:14:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,生日快樂，莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.65,0:14:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.78,0:14:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另外，希洛果然沒來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.32,0:14:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，那真的是他嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.02,0:14:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看見希洛嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.49,0:14:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，在海岸公路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.46,0:14:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，好可笑啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.03,0:14:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他正在駕駛救護車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.23,0:14:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是認錯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.70,0:14:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,救護車?不會有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.30,0:14:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼那部救護車向哪裡去了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.24,0:14:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,軍隊的港口方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.91,0:14:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜小姐，妳去哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.04,0:14:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家繼續享受派對我馬上回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.11,0:14:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去港口的話，我送妳去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.92,0:15:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，我們和妳一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.42,0:15:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.05,0:15:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別跟來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.59,0:15:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起，大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.56,0:15:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等，莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.56,0:15:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發生甚麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.40,0:15:16.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她平時不會那樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.97,0:15:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛，你想做甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.21,0:15:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要殺誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.55,0:15:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是里歐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.82,0:15:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，鋼彈在哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.79,0:15:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼回事?沒有其他金屬反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.22,0:15:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到了!我用肉眼看到了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.26,0:15:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，通知傑克斯特尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.23,0:15:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎，找到了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.23,0:15:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但嚇了我一跳，它完全沒損毀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.54,0:15:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.24,0:15:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,製造出難以想像的怪物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.44,0:15:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，把它回收後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.34,0:16:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們也能變成怪物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.11,0:16:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心海流，我們在這深度等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.26,0:16:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，準備鋼爪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.63,0:16:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.67,0:16:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.24,0:16:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自爆裝置嗎!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.45,0:16:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.39,0:16:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是甚麼光!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.06,0:16:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人!敵人呀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.77,0:16:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.90,0:17:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然能在水裡使用熱能武器!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.84,0:17:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別看小我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.73,0:17:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贏了!我贏了!傑克斯特尉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.41,0:17:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是OZ的新型機，真難應付
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.28,0:17:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是聯合的目標嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.33,0:17:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自爆裝置!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.89,0:17:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和我的機體一模一樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.47,0:18:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連自爆裝置的位置也一樣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.21,0:18:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用毀掉它啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.44,0:18:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我當備用零件機吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.36,0:18:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點!運走死傷者!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.90,0:18:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,救傷隊!\N你們在做甚麼?快點!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.27,0:18:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼事!?\N為何沒有救護隊!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.48,0:18:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.62,0:18:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.09,0:19:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行啊，希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.33,0:19:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛，你在做甚麼?告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.07,0:19:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是甚麼人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.84,0:19:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是魚雷吧，我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.04,0:19:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想知道你的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.98,0:19:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說話，希洛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.18,0:19:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.88,0:19:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.69,0:19:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳太多事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.26,0:19:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見，莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.74,0:19:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.81,0:19:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼人!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.74,0:19:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這情形怎樣看\N你也比較像壞人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.71,0:19:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒受傷吧?小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.28,0:20:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事吧?希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.63,0:20:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別勉強啊，因為你是傷者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.93,0:20:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.27,0:20:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你和這個人有何仇怨?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.77,0:20:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.78,0:20:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡，我反而變成壞人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.48,0:20:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經來了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.29,0:20:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我計算錯誤嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.16,0:20:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.93,0:20:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.23,0:20:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐，雖然好像有點內情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.30,0:20:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但立即離開這裡比較好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.54,0:20:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是為了妳的安全著想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.67,0:20:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還要來嗎!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.24,0:20:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是我的機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.25,0:21:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你做甚麼!笨蛋!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.86,0:21:17.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣，一切完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.40,0:21:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,任務完成了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.82,0:21:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙知道\N鋼彈合金的破壞數值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.19,0:21:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那機動戰士的駕駛員\N就是這傢伙嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.73,0:21:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這兩個人是甚麼人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.17,0:21:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯特尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.43,0:21:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坎沙和派西斯也沒有回音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.77,0:22:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.87,0:22:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看過鋼彈一眼的人
